## What This Rule Does Not Override

This rule adds a sequencing, audit, and gate layer. It does not replace:

| Rule | Still governs |
|---|---|
| `story-driven-development.mdc` | Story scope boundaries and scope expansion protocol |
| `workflow.mdc` | Architecture discussion, code review gate, and documentation update within each story |
| `mvp-guardrail.mdc` | Implementation complexity and abstraction decisions |
| `product-owner.mdc` | Whether a story should be built at all |
